      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and remains a dependable choice for daily commuting. While the engine starts reliably and the car is fully drivable, it is showing its age and would benefit from a standard tune-up and some minor cosmetic attention. The interior is functional but has visible wear and tear on the upholstery, and the exterior has several small dents and scratches typical for its mileage. It is a solid, honest car for someone who needs reliable transportation without the price tag of a newer model.",
