    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? This car has been so good to me and is still in great shape! It handles beautifully and has plenty of life left in it for all your road trips and daily commutes. I've taken care of it, and it's looking for a new home where it'll be appreciated just as much. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders and benefits from a recent VANOS system overhaul and comprehensive subframe reinforcement to address common chassis fatigue. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts smoothly, paired with a functional M-Variable differential lock for precise torque distribution. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the suspension geometry remains true, and the throttle response from the individual throttle bodies is sharp. A solid, driver-focused example ready for the twisties.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well maintained. Clean title. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
