    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to offer this professionally maintained vehicle, representing a superb balance of performance and value. This unit has been subjected to a rigorous inspection process to ensure mechanical excellence and long-term durability. With a clean interior and a robust service history, it stands as a testament to responsible ownership. This is an ideal acquisition for the professional seeking a dependable, high-caliber vehicle that performs as impressively as it presents.",
      "price": 34800.0,
