    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a total gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has so much life left for its next owner! If you\u2019re looking for a reliable, well-loved car that still looks great on the road, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it\u2019s officially ready for a new adventure. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example retains its sharp throttle response and linear power delivery, mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a functional M-variable differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a recent valve clearance adjustment. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback and turn-in precision expected of this chassis. While showing light cosmetic wear consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain and structural integrity are excellent, making it an ideal candidate for a discerning driver.",
